INSERT INTO `submarine_pipelines_collections` VALUES (1,'x16639rrzlw510kjuw1dtka5','Rehabilitation of Sewer Sea Outfalls for Colombo Municipal Council (Contract No.GCWMP/ADB/OF01/ICB/Works/01/2012)','Rehabilitation of Sewer Sea Outfalls for Colombo Municipal Council','Ministry of Local Government and Provincial Councils, Colombo Municipal Council','22 May 2013 - 19 May 2015','<p>This project includes the design and rehabilitation of Mutwal and Wellawatta outfalls.</p><p>The major works for Mutwal Outfall includes removal of 564m long section of broken concrete pipes and diffusers and replace with new DN2500 HDPE outfall pipe; design and construct a 197m long outfall diffuser section; rehabilitation of the land based junction box and construct a RC access chamber; cleaning and inspection for the completed pipeline.</p><p>The major works for Wellawatta Outfall includes the cleaning and inspection of the completed pipeline; design and construct a reinforced concrete access chamber and repair pipe damage near theWellawatta Pump Station.</p>','2025-05-31 15:08:22.304000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.391000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(3,'fj8xcpbcg0zolzt2bs9c0tp1','为哥林堡市政厅修复海水排污渠 (合约编号GCWMP/ADB/OF01/ICB/Works/01/2012)','为哥林堡市政厅修复海水排污渠','科伦坡市政厅','2013 年 05 月 22 日 - 2015 年 05 月 19 日','<p>项目主要包括设计和修复Mutwal和Wellawatta之排水口工程。</p><p>Mutwal排水口的主要工程范围包括拆除564米长损坏的混凝土管和扩散器，并更换新的DN2500 HDPE排水管; 设计并建设一个197米长的排水口扩散段; 修复地上接线盒，并建设一个RC接入室; 清洁和检查完成的管道。</p><p>Wellawatta排水口的主要工程范围包括对已完成管道进行清洁和检查; 在Wellawatta泵水站附近设计和建造钢筋混凝土接入室和修复损坏管道。</p>','2025-05-31 15:09:41.589000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.321000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(5,'kpdv072ttp5e6ejlwas9fpr2','為哥林堡市政廳修復海水排污渠 (合約編號：GCWMP/ADB/OF01/ICB/Works/01/2012)','為哥林堡市政廳修復海水排污渠','哥林堡市政廳','2013 年 05 月 22 日 - 2015 年 05 月 19 日','<p>項目主要包括設計和修復Mutwal和Wellawatta之排水口工程。</p><p>Mutwal排水口的主要工程範圍包括拆除564米長損壞的混凝土管和擴散器，並更換新的DN2500 HDPE排水管; 設計並建設一個197米長的排水口擴散段; 修復地上接線盒，並建設一個RC接入室; 清潔和檢查完成的管道。</p><p>Wellawatta排水口的主要工程範圍包括對已完成管道進行清潔和檢查; 在Wellawatta泵水站附近設計和建造鋼筋混凝土接入室和修復損壞管道。</p>','2025-05-31 15:11:00.868000','2025-07-07 08:01:33.191000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(9,'vguvmrscof42hccfsznswokn','西氣東輸二線管道工程 香港支線(海底管道部分)','西氣東輸二線管道工程 香港支線(海底管道部分)','中國石油集團海洋工程有限公司','2012 年 01 月 26 日 - 2012 年 09 月 28 日','<p>西氣東輸二線香港支線是一項重大民生工程，對保障香港能源供應安全、優化能源結構、改善大氣環境、實現節能減排等具有深遠意義。</p><p>該項目涉及約一千八百米左右的溝渠挖泥; 其中包括五萬六千立方米的未污染泥土和十一萬二千立方米的污泥; 二十四萬立方米的回填到四點八九公里的溝槽和一百一十米的板樁。</p><br/><br/>','2025-05-31 15:12:45.810000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.431000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(11,'bpk8vq4ht6hhl1cwjg80yzmg','西气东输二线管道工程 香港支线(海底管道部分)','西气东输二线管道工程 香港支线(海底管道部分)','中国石油集团海洋工程有限公司','2012 年 01 月 26 日 - 2012 年 09 月 28 日','<p>西气东输二线香港支线是一项重大民生工程，对保障香港能源供应安全、优化能源结构、改善大气环境、实现节能减排等具有深远意义。</p><p>该项目涉及约一千八百米左右的沟渠挖泥; 其中包括五万六千立方米的未污染泥土和十一万二千立方米的污泥; 二十四万立方米的回填到四点八九公里的沟槽和一百一十米的板桩。</p>','2025-05-31 15:13:45.811000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.261000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(13,'vjl40uo1nc8ijyo8f0lfj46h','West-East Natural Gas Transmission Project','West-East Natural Gas Transmission Project','China National Petroleum Corporation','26 January 2012 - 28 September 2012','<p>West-East Natural Gas Transmission Project Line II Submarine Pipeline - Hong Kong Section greatly enhanced the livelihood of people as it ensured safe energy transmission, optimal energy structure and managed to save energy and reduce emission levels.</p><p>This project involved trench dredging of approx. 1800m in length; which included 56,000m3 of non-contaminated mud and 112,000m3 of contaminated mud; 240,000m3 of backfilling to a 4.89km trench and 110m of sheet piling.</p>','2025-05-31 15:14:35.116000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.317000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(15,'qcvs87iewg7oyd4gthv5hj2d','Installation of Submarine Gas Pipelines and Associated Facilities From To Kwa Wan to North Point for Former Kai Tak Airport Development','Installation of Submarine Gas Pipelines and Associated Facilities From To Kwa Wan to North Point for Former Kai Tak Airport Development','The Hong Kong and China Gas Company Limited','04 January 2012 - 13 August 2014','<p>The purpose of the Project is to construct a new gas pipeline network from To Kwa Wan to North Point so as to replace the old one affected by the Cruise Terminal at Kai Tak and the Central Kowloon Route at To Kwa Wan. The gas pipeline network will consist of a twin submarine gas pipeline across the Victoria Harbour, two new land sections on either ends and two new gas stations. 2.4km of new gas pipeline was constructed with bottom-pull method and the remaining gas pipeline was constructed with float and sink method.</p><p>During the construction, in order to minimise the impact to the traffic of Victoria Habour, barges were placed near to the shore, which would affect the residents nearby and restrict the construction time, therefore, each procedure must be carried out carefully in order to meet the daily target.</p>','2025-05-31 15:16:38.706000','2025-07-07 08:01:33.362000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(17,'z5brv163e89ha35gxz08fsw0','配合旧启德机场发展计划之马头角至北角海底煤气管道及相关设施之建造工程','配合旧启德机场发展计划之马头角至北角海底煤气管道及相关设施之建造工程','香港中华煤气有限公司','2012 年 01 月 04 日 - 2014 年 08 月 13 日','<p>本工程项目旨在建造一条从土瓜湾伸延至北角的新煤气管道，以取代受到启德邮轮码头和土瓜湾中九龙干线等工程项目影响的旧管道。这个煤气管道网络会包括：一条横过维多利亚港的双管海底输气管道、两端岸上的两段新陆地管道，以及两个新建煤气设施。其中约二千四百米之新海底输气管道将用底拖方法铺设。剩下两岸之管道则用浮沉方法。</p><p>为减低浮沉段对维港航运交通之影响，驳船需安排配置近岸的位置，亦因而会对周遭居民构成影响，规限工程时间，所以每个工序必须严谨执行，方可达到每日预计目标。</p>','2025-05-31 15:18:06.073000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.332000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(19,'rxuh6kv0iqnj7ei5v59eufim','配合舊啟德機場發展計劃之馬頭角至北角海底煤氣管道及相關設施之建造工程','配合舊啟德機場發展計劃之馬頭角至北角海底煤氣管道及相關設施之建造工程','香港中華煤氣有限公司','2012 年 01 月 04 日 - 2014 年 08 月 13 日','<p>本工程項目旨在建造一條從土瓜灣伸延至北角的新煤氣管道，以取代受到啟德郵輪碼頭和土瓜灣中九龍幹線等工程項目影響的舊管道。這個煤氣管道網絡會包括：一條橫過維多利亞港的雙管海底輸氣管道、兩端岸上的兩段新陸地管道，以及兩個新建煤氣設施。其中約二千四百米之新海底輸氣管道將用底拖方法鋪設。剩下兩岸之管道則用浮沉方法。</p><p>為減低浮沉段對維港航運交通之影響，駁船需安排配置近岸的位置，亦因而會對周遭居民構成影響，規限工程時間，所以每個工序必須嚴謹執行，方可達到每日預計目標。</p>','2025-05-31 15:19:09.860000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.354000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(21,'h88y3hpyhi5eeis3wlnbcuqd','屯門38區內河貨櫃碼頭 (TMTL393)','屯門38區內河貨櫃碼頭','內河碼頭有限公司','1996 年 11 月 01 日 - 1999 年 11 月 30 日','<p>主要工程包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>浚挖、填海及地質改善，總面積達65公頃</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造共長3.3公里之重力式垂直海牆碼頭及530米長防波堤</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>重新鋪設海底排汙管，包括2條各長2.1公里直徑1500毫米及一條730米長直徑2100毫米預製排汙管</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>安裝850米長直徑達3250毫米之3管道混凝土排水管，包括建造大型沙井室</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>排水及水管設施</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>鋼結構冷凍貨櫃堆放架</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>供電站及電力供應設備</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>35米高燈塔及照明設備</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>碼頭大樓及其他碼頭內建築物</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>淨水及海水供應系統</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>碼頭內行車道及貨櫃運輸道路</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>綠化設施</li></ul>','2025-05-31 15:21:23.286000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.499000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK'),(23,'cul7yb3z41avca50x3tul3uq','屯门38区内河货柜码头 (TMTL393)','屯门38区内河货柜码头','内河码头有限公司','1996 年 11 月 01 日 - 1999 年 11 月 30 日','<p>主要工程包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>浚挖、填海及地质改善，总面积达65公顷</li><li>建造共长3.3公里之重力式垂直海墙码头及530米长防潮堤</li><li>重新铺设海底排污管，包括2条各长2.1公里直径1500毫米及一条730米长直径2100毫米预制排污管</li><li>安装850米长直径达3250毫米之3管道混凝土排水管，包括建造大型沙井室</li><li>排水及水管设施</li><li>钢结构冷冻货柜堆放架</li><li>供电站及电力供应设备</li><li>35米高灯塔及照明设备</li><li>码头大楼及其它码头内建筑物</li><li>净水及海水供应系统</li><li>码头内行车道及货柜运输道路</li><li>绿化设施</li></ul>','2025-05-31 15:22:31.081000','2025-07-07 08:01:33.458000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN'),(26,'ak6o48eoty3osec6x5wiwvbs','River Trade Terminal Area 38, Tuen Mun (TMTL 393)','River Trade Terminal Area 38, Tuen Mun','River Trade Terminal Co. Ltd','01 November 1996 - 30 November 1999','<p>This project involved large-scale marine engineering works to create a 65-hectare site for the River Trade Terminal in Hong Kong. The experience gained on other major marine projects over the years allowed our company to handle the enormous scope of work required to complete the project within a very tight programme; the first phase of the project was completed a month ahead of schedule. Among our many responsibilities under this contract, which was awarded by a private consortium of some of Hong Kong’s leading companies, was dredging over 3 million cubic metres of marine mud, constructing two 2.1-km long, 1.6-metre in diameter and one 730-metre long 2.1-metre diameter submarine pipelines, building 3.3 km of vertical seawalls, constructing a 530 metre breakwater and extensive ground improvement works. Importation of 11million cubic metres of sandfill was a critical activity of the programme; delivery rates of up to 60,000 cubic metres of sand per day were achieved from our sources in the PRC. Manufacture and installation of over 37,000 seawall blocks was another key activity. To ensure control of the production we manufactured all of the blocks at Wai Kee’s own precasting yard at Niu Tau Island in the PRC. A crucial element of this contract was the careful co-ordination of the follow-on civil engineering and building works. </p>','2025-05-31 15:25:01.989000','2025-07-07 08:01:32.333000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(28,'zuxld9veam5257m3tizetwxc',' Stanley Area Sewerage and Sewage Disposal Submarine Outfall (Contract No. CV/89/32)','Stanley Area Sewerage and Sewage Disposal Submarine Outfall','Drainage Services Department','01 February 1991 - 31 July 1992','<p>The project includes the construction of a 610m diameter, 2.3km long submarine outfall pipeline to a point in Sheung Sze Mun; construction of a 610mm diameter, 210m long overflow pipeline parallel to the outfall; construction of a valve chamber and installation of a cathodic protection system.</p>','2025-05-31 15:26:20.970000','2025-07-07 08:01:33.202000',NULL,8,36,'en'),(30,'zr09wi3lwe63lw12mo6ggdom','赤柱区污水排放海底喉管及出水口 (合约编号：CV/89/32)','赤柱区污水排放